docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs help - Print this help message. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. for word in lista: print(word).lower def replaceCharacters(message, delimiter, character): messagem = message.replace(delimiter, character).lower() return messagem if 10 > 2: print(Maior)
